FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FDetectives have informed the trust's
OL,7,Fbosses and told them to preserve all
OL,8,Frecords related to the June 2023
OL,9,Fattacks.
OL,11,FThe trust said that it would co-
OL,12,Foperate with the inquiry.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FEmma Webber, mother of University of
OL,7,FNottingham history student Barnaby,
OL,8,Fwho was killed alongside his friend Ms
OL,9,FO'Malley-Kumar as they walked back to
OL,10,Ftheir accommodation after going out to
OL,11,Fcelebrate the end of the academic
OL,12,Fyear, said the police investigation
OL,13,Fsignifies "the beginning of the
OL,14,Freckoning".
OL,16,FShe added that this will send "much-
OL,17,Fneeded shockwaves across our public
OL,18,Fservices".
OL,26,@uD@KOUvD@JO]xD@_OUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FCalocane, who was under the care of
OL,7,FNHFT from 2020 until 2022, had a
OL,8,Frucksack of weapons when he fatally
OL,9,Fstabbed students Barnaby Webber and
OL,10,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, and
OL,11,Fcaretaker Ian Coates, 65, in
OL,12,FNottingham in the early hours of June
OL,13,F13 2023.
OL,15,FHe then attempted to murder three
OL,16,Fpedestrians in Nottingham city centre
OL,17,Fusing a van he stole from Mr Coates,
OL,18,Fleaving them seriously injured.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FCalocane was sentenced to an
OL,7,Findefinite hospital order after he
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to manslaughter and
OL,9,Fattempted murder.
OL,11,FThe former mechanical engineering
OL,12,Fstudent had been sectioned four times
OL,13,Fwhile under the care of NHFT, before
OL,14,Fhe was discharged to his GP.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FA public inquiry, which looked at
OL,7,Fevents leading up to the killings,
OL,8,Fheard he was discharged by the trust's
OL,9,FEarly Intervention in Psychosis (EIP)
OL,10,Fservice because he failed to turn up
OL,11,Ffor appointments and the team had
OL,12,F"lost" him.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for NHFT confirmed that
OL,15,FNorthumbria Police, acting on behalf
OL,16,Fof Nottinghamshire Police, had started
OL,17,Fan investigation.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FIn a statement on Wednesday morning,
OL,7,FMrs Webber said: "The news that
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Mental Health Trust is
OL,9,Fbeing investigated for corporate
OL,10,Fmanslaughter is an unprecedented move
OL,11,Fthat will send much-needed shockwaves
OL,12,Facross our public services, and in
OL,13,Fparticular the NHS.
OL,15,F"We have been aware this was being
OL,16,Fconsidered since December 2025, and a
OL,17,Fnumber of weeks ago were told,
OL,18,Ffollowing a meeting with Northumbria
OL,19,FPolice, who will be leading the
OL,20,Finvestigation, that the very high
OL,21,Fthreshold and bar had been met.
OL,26,@oD@ROUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,F"This means a full investigation with
OL,7,Fthe involvement of the CPS will now
OL,8,Fcommence, and that accountability at
OL,9,Fthe organisational level we have been
OL,10,Fcalling for is beginning.
OL,12,F"This has to be the line in the sand `
OL,13,Fwhen those who fail, neglect and cover
OL,14,Fup, from the leaders at the top down,
OL,15,Fare fully held to account and made to
OL,16,Frecognise their failures.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,F"This includes chief executives,
OL,7,Fchairmen of the board, non-executive
OL,8,Fand executive board members, as well
OL,9,Fas the negligent clinicians,
OL,10,Fpractitioners and hospital managers
OL,11,Fwho over a sustained period failed to
OL,12,Fmanage and recognise the threat posed
OL,13,Fby Valdo Calocane.
OL,15,F"They chose to allow him to dictate
OL,16,Fwhat was happening, and therefore
OL,17,Ffailed to treat a man who refused
OL,18,Ftreatment, allowing him to go on to
OL,19,Fcommit the murder and take the lives
OL,20,Fof three innocent souls.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,F"This statement today brings us no
OL,7,Fjoy, but it does signify the beginning
OL,8,Fof the reckoning ` in Barney's memory,
OL,9,Fin Grace's memory and in Ian's memory,
OL,10,Fand for the protection of those in the
OL,11,Ffuture who could face another Valdo
OL,12,FCalocane.
OL,14,F"We now ask that, for the first time,
OL,15,Fall of those involved who will be
OL,16,Frequired to participate do so with
OL,17,Ffull candour and transparency."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@_O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FThe public inquiry into the attacks,
OL,7,Fwhich lasted more than three months
OL,8,Fand heard from 164 witnesses, finished
OL,9,Fin June and chairwoman Her Honour
OL,10,FDeborah Taylor is expected to report
OL,11,Fback with her findings and
OL,12,Frecommendations next year.
OL,14,FIn a statement, NHFT said it would be
OL,15,F"co-operating fully" with the police
OL,16,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,FA spokesman said: "Northumbria Police,
OL,7,Facting on behalf of Nottinghamshire
OL,8,FPolice, have begun an investigation
OL,9,Finto matters relating to the care and
OL,10,Ftreatment of Valdo Calocane.
OL,12,F"We know how important the independent
OL,13,Finquiry and police investigation are
OL,14,Ffor the affected families, the
OL,15,Fsurvivors and our local communities.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,344,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F343A1784735286
OL,3,CCorporate manslaughter probe for NHS
OL,4,Ctrust responsible for triple killer
OL,6,F"We will, of course, be co-operating
OL,7,Ffully with Northumbria Police, as we
OL,8,Fhave with the Statutory Inquiry into
OL,9,Fthese matters which is being chaired
OL,10,Fby Her Honour Deborah Taylor, and
OL,11,Fwhich will hear final submissions from
OL,12,Fall the parties involved later this
OL,13,Fyear."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G13/13
